Step 1: Make sure your project files are ready 
Step 2: Go to the dev folder
Step 3: cd /terraform/envs/dev
Step 4: Initialize terraform >> terraform init
Step 5: Validate the configuration >> terraform validate  # checks for syntax and module references
Step 6: Create a Plan >> terraform plan -out plan.tfplan
Step 7: Apply the plan >> terraform apply plan.tfplan 
  
